defs.name: cswap
defs.value: fn <T> (x: T, y: T, c: T) -> (T, T)
defs.docs:
Conditional, constant-time swapping.
 Returns `(x, y)` if `c == 0` and `(y, x)` if `c == T::max`.
 The return value is undefined if `c` has any other value.
